name: Baedal-Minjok fonts
description:
Baedal-Minjok fonts are decorative Korean font families. They are intentionally designed to look old-styled. They are designed for "Baedal-Minjok" food delivery service.

This package includes 10 font families; BM HANNA 11yrs old, BMHANNAAir, BMHANNAPro, BM JUA, BM DoHyeon, BM YEONSUNG, BM KIRANGHAERANG, BM EULJIRO, BM EULJITO 10 YEARS LATER and BM EULJIRO ORAEORAE.
